<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Przypomnienie o spotkaniu</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      background-color: #0f0e17;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #e2e0f0;
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #1a1827;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #2e2a45;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6d28d9 0%, #a855f7 100%);
      padding: 32px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header__logo {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body__greeting {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #c4b5fd !important;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .body__text {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #b0aac8;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .highlight {
      background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.25);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #c4b5fd;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .btn-wrapper { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #a855f7);
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      border-radius: 50px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 24px 40px;
      background: #15121f;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #4a4462;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6d28d9 0%,#a855f7 100%);color:#ffffff !important;">
      <div class="header__logo" style="color:#ffffff !important;">e<span style="color:#e9d5ff !important;">Wróżka</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p class="body__greeting" style="color:#c4b5fd;">Cześć, {{recipientName}}! ✨</p>
      <p class="body__text" style="color:#b0aac8;">
        Przypominamy – Twoje spotkanie z <strong>{{wizardName}}</strong> ({{adTitle}}) odbędzie się za <strong>{{hoursLabel}}</strong>.
      </p>
      <div class="highlight" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.25);color:#c4b5fd !important;">
        <strong style="color:#e2e0f0 !important;">{{scheduledAt}}</strong><br />
        Czas trwania: {{durationMinutes}} min
      </div>
      <div class="btn-wrapper">
        <a href="{{meetingUrl}}" class="btn">Wejdź do spotkania</a>
      </div>
      <p class="body__text" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #8b7aa8;">
        Link będzie aktywny od 15 minut przed rozpoczęciem spotkania.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">© eWróżka · Do zobaczenia na spotkaniu!</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
